                "• Cookie有效期有限，过期后需重新配置\n" +
                "• 会员视频仍需账号有相应权限\n" +
                "• 如遇下载失败，优先使用「导入本地视频」",
                style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,
                color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurfaceVariant
            )

            Spacer(Modifier.height(32.dp))
        }
    }

    // Cookie获取帮助对话框
    if (showCookieHelp) {
        AlertDialog(
            onDismissRequest = { showCookieHelp = false },
            title = { Text("如何获取B站Cookie") },
            text = {
                Column(modifier = Modifier.verticalScroll(rememberScrollState())) {
                    Text("方法一：使用浏览器开发者工具", style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleSmall)
                    Text(
                        "1. 在浏览器中登录 bilibili.com\n" +
                        "2. 按 F12 打开开发者工具\n" +
                        "3. 切换到 Application (应用) 标签\n" +
                        "4. 左侧选择 Cookies → https://www.bilibili.com\n" +
                        "5. 找到 SESSDATA 的值，复制填写",
                        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall
                    )

                    Spacer(Modifier.height(12.dp))

                    Text("方法二：使用浏览器插件", style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleSmall)
                    Text(
                        "1. 安装 \"EditThisCookie\" 等Cookie管理插件\n" +
                        "2. 访问 bilibili.com 并登录\n" +
                        "3. 点击插件图标，找到 SESSDATA 值",
                        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall
                    )

                    Spacer(Modifier.height(12.dp))

                    Text("方法三：自动获取（推荐）", style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleSmall)
                    Text(
                        "点击SESSDATA输入框右侧的「自动获取」按钮，\n" +
                        "在弹出的页面中完成登录即可自动获取Cookie",
                        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,
                        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primary
                    )

                    Spacer(Modifier.height(12.dp))

                    Text("说明：", style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleSmall)
                    Text(
                        "• SESSDATA 是必填项，包含登录状态\n" +
                        "• bili_jct 和 DedeUserID 可选，但建议填写\n" +
                        "• Cookie有有效期，过期需重新获取",
                        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,
                        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurfaceVariant
                    )
                }
            },
            confirmButton = {
                TextButton(onClick = { showCookieHelp = false }) {
                    Text("知道了")
                }
            }
        )
    }

    // B站登录对话框
    if (showBilibiliLogin) {
        BilibiliLoginDialog(
            onDismiss = { showBilibiliLogin = false },
            onCookiesExtracted = { cookies ->
                // 自动填充获取到的Cookie
                cookies.sessdata?.let { viewModel.setBilibiliSessdata(it) }
                cookies.biliJct?.let { viewModel.setBilibiliBiliJct(it) }
                cookies.dedeUserID?.let { viewModel.setBilibiliDedeuserid(it) }
                // 自动启用Cookie认证
                viewModel.setEnableCookieAuth(true)
            }
        )
    }
}

